data.title: Elena Ledoux's Husband
data.meta_description: Elena Ledoux’s husband is James Kerr,  tech entrepreneur and adventurer.
data.meta_site_name: House Cleaning Services | House Cleaners in Las Vegas NV | Superb Maids
data.text:
James Kerr is a tech entrepreneur and philanthropist. He’s founder and Chief Geek of SuperGeeks, a multinational consulting firm which helps companies leverage new business opportunities. Services include sales, strategic initiatives, business partnerships, market development, business expansion, and marketing.

James' latest startup is Boss Security Screens.

A farm boy from Maryland, James lives in Las Vegas but frequently travels to speak to industry groups about emerging technologies. He’s also a go-to IT expert for a wide array of media outlets. James is the author of three books, sits on several nonprofit boards and founded a mentoring program for at-risk youth.

When he’s not spending time with his family, James enjoys flying, sailing, playing chess and teaching the martial arts.
